Introduction

9MUSES A is the sub-group of 9MUSES formed by Star Empire Entertainment in 2016. The unit debuted on August 4, 2016, with the single MUSES DIARY.

On February 10, 2019, it was announced that 9MUSES had disbanded after nine years due to the expiration of the member's contracts.

On March 21, 2023, it was reported that 9MUSES A would be reuniting and making a comeback in May.
